,,23312,,"STETSON | FLATROCK | STRAW HAT | NATURAL/BURNT | SSFLTR-7434BUXL","STETSON | FLATROCK | STRAW HAT | NATURAL/BURNT | SSFLTR-7434BUXL",stetson-flatrock-shapeable-straw-cowboy-hat-ssfltr-7434buxl-2,https://cuevaswesternwear.com/shop/hats/straw-hats/stetson-flatrock-shapeable-straw-cowboy-hat-ssfltr-7434buxl-2/,https://cuevaswesternwear.com/shop/hats/straw-hats/stetson-flatrock-shapeable-straw-cowboy-hat-ssfltr-7434buxl-2/,"The STETSON Flatrock Cowboy Hat is the perfect hat for any outfit if you need a comfortable hat to shade your eyes from the sun. Made of premium raffia straw, it is lightweight and breathable which allows your skin to breathe for all-day comfort. Featuring a 3 1/2″ shapeable brim that offers ample coverage from the sun’s glaring light, this headgear keeps your noggin cool to let you enjoy adventures outdoors. This shapeable hat features a braided leather hatband adorned with turquoise concho.

Stetson is the standard in hats, the essence of the spirit of the West, and an icon of everyday American lifestyle. Because of its authentic American heritage, Stetson remains a part of history and, for the same reason will continue into the future. Stetson, it’s not just a hat, it’s the hat.

,,22987,,"DURANGO |  MEN'S REBEL PRO|COFFEE WESTERN BOOT| BROWN-DDB0290","DURANGO |  MEN'S REBEL PRO|COFFEE WESTERN BOOT| BROWN-DDB0290",durango-rebel-pro-coffee-western-boot-ddb0290-2,https://cuevaswesternwear.com/shop/men/work-boots/durango-rebel-pro-coffee-western-boot-ddb0290-2/,https://cuevaswesternwear.com/shop/men/work-boots/durango-rebel-pro-coffee-western-boot-ddb0290-2/,"This is the men's 12"" Western Coffee/Bone Durango® Rebel Pro™ style.

This style is full grain leather with a soft mesh lining inside and has the Durango® X-Pand System™ which is a hidden gore expansion for universal fit and easy on off. This style contains a comfortable 7-layer comfort system.
The first layer is the Durango® X-Treme Comfort Footbed™ with memory foam for all day comfort and support.
The second layer is an EVA cushion layer that contours and molds to your foot.
The third layer is a ¾ genuine Goodyear® welt construction and a genuine leather welt with double row cotton stitch.
The fourth layer is a two-layer innersole with a flexible full-length bottom and stabilizing rigid ¾ heel tuck.

The fifth layer is the patented Dually shank system™ which contains two fiberglass shanks for medial and lateral torsion stability and midfoot support. The littleway stitch binds the outsole, heel tuck, and upper for absolute durability.
The sixth layer is the ABS heel base which is nailed-weight relieved for lightweight durability.

The seventh layer is the slip, oil and abrasion resistant rubber outsole that offers instant gratification. The 1 ½"" rocker heel lessens stress by promoting a more natural heel strike and the rolled shank area is perfect for stirrup- friendly ease.

Unbridle your western spirit in the men's 12"" Western Coffee/Bone Durango® Rebel Pro™; the perfect boots for performance-driven individuals. ,,21047,,"DURANGO | MEN'S STEEL TOE WATERPROOF WESTERN BOOT | BROWN/TAN -DB019","DURANGO | MEN'S STEEL TOE WATERPROOF WESTERN BOOT | BROWN/TAN -DB019",rebel-by-durango-steel-toe-waterproof-western-boot-db019-2,https://cuevaswesternwear.com/shop/men/work-boots/rebel-by-durango-steel-toe-waterproof-western-boot-db019-2/,https://cuevaswesternwear.com/shop/men/work-boots/rebel-by-durango-steel-toe-waterproof-western-boot-db019-2/,"This men's 11"" square-toe Western boot is part of the Rebel™ by Durango® collection, so you can be certain that it will be lightweight, comfortable to wear and outstandingly durable. Its upper has been constructed out of full-grain leather; the slight distressing, handsome stitching and combination of burnt yellow and brown hues creates a very nice looking men's boot. Having finger holes, pull straps and a slightly dipped topline allow you to pull these Western boots on with absolute ease.

Complying with the ASTM F2413 Protective Toe Classification and the ASTM F2413 Electrical Hazard Standard allows these steel-toe boots to offer you optimal protection against dropped objects and also keep the bottoms of your feet safe when stepping down on top of electrical equipment.

column2: • Pull on your patriotic pride in this men’s 11"" American Flag Rebel™ by Durango® style. The look, level of comfort, and heel height are ideal for you!The foot and trim are made from oiled, dark brown full-grain leather. The square toe adds a very traditional flair to this western boot, but the focal point is the shaft, which proudly displays the American flag. The footbed will provide cushioning, ease the weight of your steps and it circulates the air within these boots. Eau de Parfums therefore last longer and smell more intense. Natural or synthetic fragrances? Perfumes with natural ingredients often smell different in batches based on the source of the ingredients, while synthetic ingredients usually have consistency in their smell and lasts longer. Notes and different smell after application? Perfumes are often designed with top, middle and base notes, and designed to smell different based on the time after application. For example, some top note citrus scents smell stronger immediately upon application, while a lavender middle note may be sensed after some time from application as the top note evaporates.
